description:
This table `EUtranCellTDD` stores configuration parameters for E-UTRAN Time Division Duplex (TDD) cells.

- `dateTime`: Timestamp of the configuration data.
- `Area_Name`: Name of the geographical area where the cell is located.
- `CellId`: Unique identifier of the E-UTRAN cell.
- `Id2`: Duplicate of CellId.
- `Id3`:  Another identifier potentially related to the cell, possibly a more granular identifier or a different naming convention.
- `vsDataType`:  Indicates the type of data, specifically E-UTRAN TDD cell data.
- `vsDataFormatVersion`: Version of the data format used.
- `EUtranCellTDD.ns05LowBandSchedMode`: Scheduling mode for low-band in NS05.
- `EUtranCellTDD.tPollRetxRrcReleaseDl`: Downlink RRC release poll retransmission timer.
- `EUtranCellTDD.upperLayerAutoConfEnabled`: Flag indicating if upper layer auto-configuration is enabled.
- `EUtranCellTDD.cceDynUeAdmCtrlOverloadThr`: Overload threshold for dynamic UE admission control using CCEs.
- `EUtranCellTDD.aiAdvCellSupMode`: Mode of advanced interference suppression.
- `EUtranCellTDD.dynUeAdmCtrlEnabled`: Flag indicating if dynamic UE admission control is enabled.
- `EUtranCellTDD.outOfCoverageThreshold`: Threshold for out-of-coverage conditions.
- `EUtranCellTDD.optimizedPdcchCongestThres`: Optimized PDCCH congestion threshold.
- `EUtranCellTDD.freqBand`: Frequency band of the cell.
- `EUtranCellTDD.plmn1AbConfProfileRef`: Reference to PLMN1 access barring configuration profile.
- `EUtranCellTDD.cellCapMaxCellSubCap`: Maximum cell capacity for cell sub-capacity.
- `EUtranCellTDD.loadBasedCaEnabled`: Flag indicating if load-based carrier aggregation is enabled.
- `EUtranCellTDD.servOrPrioIFHoSetupBearer`: Flag indicating if service or priority Inter-Frequency handover (IFHO) setup bearer is enabled.
- `EUtranCellTDD.rtpTimeout`: RTP timeout value.
- `EUtranCellTDD.uncertSemiMajor`: Uncertainty in semi-major axis.
- `EUtranCellTDD.iflbAbEnabled`: Flag indicating if Inter-Frequency Load Balancing (IFLB) access barring is enabled.
- `EUtranCellTDD.pagingPriorityDiffThr`: Paging priority difference threshold.
- `EUtranCellTDD.lbabBarringPriorityLevel`: Load balancing access barring priority level.
- `EUtranCellTDD.sCellHandlingAtVolteCall`: Handling of secondary cells during VoLTE calls.
- `EUtranCellTDD.zzzTemporary7`: Reserved for future use.
- `EUtranCellTDD.zzzTemporary8`: Reserved for future use.
